109
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:31,000
-I always go crazy?
-Clear the payment.

110
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,830
Got it? Do it immediately.

111
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:50,600
I'm not going to fucking look at this.

112
