by tomorrow.

158
00:09:57,730 --> 00:10:00,600
Ms. Sun...

159
00:10:00,690 --> 00:10:01,520
That's fine.

160
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:04,610
I'm going to the next meeting.
Let's end it here.

161
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,650
