-Yeah.

165
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:08,590
Goodness. My fate is sealed.

166
00:11:10,090 --> 00:11:13,010
Ever since Mr. Jung spoke up
against Mr. Ma,

167
00:11:13,090 --> 00:11:15,840
he seems to have a vendetta against us.

168
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:18,470
Heck, our office may be even moved
next to the toilet.

169
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:20,220
Zip it. Words can become reality.

170
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:22,060
The good days will come around,
sooner or later.

171
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:23,350
When is that day?

172
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:25,650
The day Mr. Ma retires from work?

173
00:11:25,730 --> 00:11:26,560
Hey, Hyung-ki.

174
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:28,270
Aren't you supposed to be
in London by now?

175
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,900
