is quite near, isn't it?

178
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:39,620
Well, yes.

179
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:42,790
Jeez. When Geu-rae leaves,
someone else will have a hard time.

180
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:45,040
