my part properly.

191
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:51,400
But still I thought it would be good

192
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:54,280
to be partners with someone
I'm comfortable talking to.

193
00:12:56,490 --> 00:12:57,910
I just wanted to tell you.

194
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,240
I didn't ask you to be my partner

195
