other colleagues to begin with.

204
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:45,580
Is there really no way?

205
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:48,620
That's all I think about nowadays.

206
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,000
There's no way, isn't there?

207
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:01,090
Maybe you can make it
into a company-wide agenda.

208
00:14:02,050 --> 00:14:03,100
A company-wide issue?

209
