and dwell on the issue?

211
00:14:10,810 --> 00:14:12,440
Then the company may have to reconsider.

212
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:17,190
I'm not saying that's a solution,
but it's a start.

213
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:20,860
Make it a company-wide issue?

214
00:14:20,950 --> 00:14:24,320
Right, according to Mr. Ha,
the point is to get as many employees

215
00:14:24,410 --> 00:14:26,620
as possible to understand
Geu-rae's situation.

216
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,830
That Geu-rae is an asset to the company.

217
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:32,370
That Geu-rae deserves a contract
extension.

218
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:34,040
-How?
-Yes. How?

219
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,670
