228
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:00,490
I have to try something.

229
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:03,910
I'm willing to even try the method that
made me look like an idiot in the past.

230
00:15:12,830 --> 00:15:13,870
I'm leaving too.

231
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:16,420
I think I have an idea.

232
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,500
What?

233
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:38,860
Hello, Young-yi?

234
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:41,150
Yes, Ms. Sun. I have...

235
