the last two years of his employment.

306
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:24,830
Geu-rae Jang should become
a permanent employee.

307
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:27,340
Long ago, he once told me,

308
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:31,510
