Al-Khazneh.

953
01:10:07,400 --> 01:10:08,700
The Treasury of the Pharaoh.

954
01:10:10,950 --> 01:10:12,280
The gate of Petra.

955
01:10:17,580 --> 01:10:20,170
Merchants had to pass by here.

956
01:10:22,250 --> 01:10:23,960
The Persian Gulf in the East.

957
01:10:24,710 --> 01:10:25,920
The Red Sea in the South.

958
01:10:27,010 --> 01:10:28,800
And the Mediterranean Sea in the West.

959
01:10:29,470 --> 01:10:31,640
